Madagascar Inflation Rate Falls to 8.9% in August, Agency Says

-- B y   K a m l e s h   B h u c k o r y
-- 
2011-09-19T08:30:06Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-19/madagascar-inflation-rate-falls-to-8-9-in-august-agency-says.html
Madagascar’s annual inflation rate
declined to 8.9 percent in August from 9.4 percent a month
earlier, the country’s statistics agency said.  Prices increased 0.2 percent in the month, the
Antananarivo-based Institut National de la Statistique said in a
statement e-mailed today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kamlesh Bhuckory in Port Louis at 
 kbhuckory@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
